{"TopicId":162825,"ForumId":15,"TopicTitle":"New to Unity and KSP-modelling","CreatedByName":"HuXTUS","CreatedById":178977,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-02T08:39:49Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"HuXTUS","CreatedById":178977,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-02T08:39:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m absolutely new in Unity and KSP-modelling.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI made ladder for my model, and it \u003Cem\u003Eslightly\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0work: Kerbal can grab it, but...\u00A0he starts to slide and falls down the stairs.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI tried to make the stairs big, long, narrow, short, small, put it close to the detail, far, shove inside...\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow right? Thanks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022qPmzZ-SKzSU.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://pp.userapi.com/c841320/v841320660/3fdc/qPmzZ-SKzSU.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022h13r5FxKHZs.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022283\u0022 src=\u0022https://pp.userapi.com/c841320/v841320660/3fc6/h13r5FxKHZs.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022TR3CtuNuBtw.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022311\u0022 src=\u0022https://pp.userapi.com/c841320/v841320660/3fd4/TR3CtuNuBtw.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-03T00:09:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/178977-huxtus/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022178977\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/178977-huxtus/\u0022 style=\u0022\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@HuXTUS\u003C/a\u003E I took the liberty of moving your post out of the programming area of the forum and into the modelling/discussion area, you\u0027ll get better help with this sort of thing here. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"wasml","CreatedById":120438,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-03T00:59:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMade a ladder in the past that worked using a link from this page\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/85372-mod-development-links-compilation-some-links-do-not-work-formatting-broken/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nfar enough in the past that I don\u0027t remember any specifics so can\u0027t point you in the right direction other than the ladder info on that page.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNote: Wheel info is out of date but most of the other stuff is still relevant.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"artwhaley","CreatedById":118388,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-03T07:34:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEverything LOOKS right, though it\u0027s been a while since I\u0027ve made a ladder. \u00A0But you\u0027ve got the collider pointed the right way - green arrow up, blue arrow towards ship... \u00A0 you\u0027ve got the tag... \u00A0is the \u0027part triggers\u0027 label given to layer 21? \u00A0 That is or was important at one point. \u00A0 If it\u0027s \u0027sorta\u0027 working... \u00A0my guess would be interference from other colliders pushing them off, perhaps? \u00A0 I\u0027d make sure that the colliders for your other mesh objects aren\u0027t clipping through your ladder collider making it hard for a kerbal to occupy the space? \u00A0Sometimes the mesh colliders cut corners in ways that aren\u0027t obvious when they\u0027re checked to \u0027convex\u0027.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HuXTUS","CreatedById":178977,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-03T17:26:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223109425\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022162825\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221499040578\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002212858\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Red Iron Crown\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 hours ago, Red Iron Crown said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/178977-huxtus/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022178977\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/178977-huxtus/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@HuXTUS\u003C/a\u003E I took the liberty of moving your post out of the programming area of the forum and into the modelling/discussion area, you\u0027ll get better help with this sort of thing here. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis shocked me a little and dissociated. It was as if the earth was gone from under my feet, and I found myself in an unfamiliar room. But now I\u0027m fine.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n@\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Ca data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/120438-wasml/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0026amp;referrer=http%253A%252F%252Fforum.kerbalspaceprogram.com%252Findex.php%253F%252Ftopic%252F162825-new-to-unity-and-ksp-modelling%252F\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/120438-wasml/\u0022 style=\u0022color:inherit;\u0022 title=\u0022Go to wasml\u0027s profile\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ewasml\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0@\u003Ca data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/118388-artwhaley/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0026amp;referrer=http%253A%252F%252Fforum.kerbalspaceprogram.com%252Findex.php%253F%252Ftopic%252F162825-new-to-unity-and-ksp-modelling%252F\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/118388-artwhaley/\u0022 style=\u0022color:inherit;\u0022 title=\u0022Go to artwhaley\u0027s profile\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Eartwhaley\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0thank\u00A0you.\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI looked for links and play with collider. I make the \u003Cstrong\u003Ecapsule collider\u003C/strong\u003E and move it on some distance from main collider. Hmmm...\u00A0yet it looks as if everything is normal.\u00A0Kerbal clings and crawls as I want.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022RF0eeh63t6w.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022382\u0022 src=\u0022https://pp.userapi.com/c841320/v841320660/4514/RF0eeh63t6w.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00225Uz3F8MaUYw.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022485\u0022 src=\u0022https://pp.userapi.com/c841320/v841320660/451e/5Uz3F8MaUYw.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}